 	# H1 KDE Plasma overlay
requirements:
  - wayland
  - any WM/DE that supports layer-shell (definitely not GNOME lol)
  - qdbus installed as a package (for shortcuts)
      - install: sudo dnf install qdbus
  - setting shortcut in plasma settings
      - command: qdbus org.info_overlay.Overlay /Overlay org.info_overlay.Overlay.Toggle
  












CMake Qt6 Quick Template
------------------------

You need Qt6 and CMake 3.16 or higher

-- Build instructions --

cd /home/vasik96/projects/info_overlay
mkdir build
cd build
cmake ../
make

src/info_overlay


